sp.p:

No there's the hell on't, his faith's too feeble to go alone;

hee brings flesh-flies after him, that will buzze against supper time,

and hum for his comming out.


E'en newly my Lord, iust as your Lordship enterd now;

about this place we had notice giuen hee should bee, but in some

loathsome plight or other.
